==Esperanto==
===Etymology===
Esperanto ''[[i-]]'' (indeterminate [[:Category:Esperanto correlatives|correlative]] prefix) + ''[[-es]]'' (correlative suffix of genitives)

===Correlative===
'''ies''' (''plural'' '''ies''', ''accusative singular'' '''ies''', ''accusative plural'' '''ies''')

# [[someone's]] (indeterminate correlative of genitives)
#: Like other indeterminate correlatives, '''ies''' can be combined with ''[[ajn]]'', the adverbial particle of generality. '''''Ies''' ajn'' thus means ''[[anyone's]]''.

